I don&#39;t believe EVP maker has a Mac version. The linear radio sweep method should work with any recorder or computer, it&#39;s simple and it works. Here is another example from today using EVP maker. It sounds like a diction lesson.
&quot;Dispute edited with pursuit&quot;
